briefdescription.para: The position at the front of the prepend list.

detaileddescription.para: An item added at this position will, after composition is applied, be stronger than other items prepended in this layer, and stronger than items added by weaker layers.

briefdescription.para: The position at the back of the prepend list.

detaileddescription.para: An item added at this position will, after composition is applied, be weaker than other items prepended in this layer, but stronger than items added by weaker layers.

briefdescription.para: The position at the front of the append list.

detaileddescription.para: An item added at this position will, after composition is applied, be stronger than other items appended in this layer, and stronger than items added by weaker layers.

briefdescription.para: The position at the back of the append list.

detaileddescription.para: An item added at this position will, after composition is applied, be weaker than other items appended in this layer, but stronger than items added by weaker layers.

briefdescription.para: Specifies a position to add items to lists.

detaileddescription.para: Used by some Add() methods in the USD API that manipulate lists, such as AddReference().
